00:07:24.427 --> 00:07:26.114
"Can you match the teacher's
comments to the definitions?"

00:07:26.114 --> 00:07:29.060
Duru. "The set of all points in a plane

00:07:29.060 --> 00:07:32.087
"that are the same distance
