00:07:36.516 --> 00:07:39.299
So, I would, you know,
"Stupendous! Well done."

00:07:39.299 --> 00:07:41.656
Oliver's definition.

00:07:41.656 --> 00:07:44.704
"The set of all points in 3D space

00:07:44.704 --> 00:07:47.489
"that are the same distance
from a center point."

00:07:47.489 --> 00:07:48.971
