00:07:59.557 --> 00:08:03.275
And then, finally, "A
perfectly round shape."

00:08:03.275 --> 00:08:06.118
Well, that's kind of true.

00:08:06.118 --> 00:08:07.703
But if you're talk about three dimensions,

